Class GreenNatureEntity

java.lang.Object
Entity
GreenNatureEntity
public class GreenNatureEntity
extends Entity
The GreenNatureEntity class is a Concrete Product Class. This BGreenNatureEntity represents the Green/Nature type of the game entity.
